title: The Casbah
typeOfFood: Lacto, Beer/Wine, Take-out, Middle Eastern, Non-veg
description: Serves meat, veg options available. Authentic Middle Eastern hookah lounge serves some vegetarian choices like baba ghanoush (eggplant), fool madamas (fava bean), spinach pie, vegetarian grape leaves, falafel, hummus, tabouleh, Casbah vegetarian pizza, and imjaddara (rice, lentil, onion dish with Arabic salad).
